<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="painful-adj">painful <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'peɪnfl/    美 /'peɪnfl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>令人疼痛的；引起痛苦的</strong></h4>
<p>反 painless </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My legs become painful.
我的腿开始疼了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Learning English as a second language can be a <strong>painful experience</strong>.
把英语作为第二语言来学习是一段痛苦的经历。</p><footer>2019 全国</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>painfully /'peɪnfəli/ adv   </p></div>